# App Design Guidelines — Legal AI AR (PwC)

**Full reference**: [`docs/mockups/legal-ai-ar-pwc-design-guidelines.md`](docs/mockups/legal-ai-ar-pwc-design-guidelines.md)

When building or modifying UI components, follow the PwC design system:

## Shell
- Three-zone layout: fixed header (64px), sidebar (280px), main content
- Header: `rgba(30,30,30,0.96)`, glassmorphism, z-index 200
- Sidebar: `#191919`, never collapses on desktop

## Colors
- Primary: `#D04A02` (orange), hover `#EB8C00` (amber)
- Page bg: `#f3f3f3`; cards: `#ffffff`; borders: `#d1d1d1`
- Text: `#252525` (headings), `#474747` (body), `#696969` (secondary)

## Typography
- Headings: Georgia; UI/body: Arial
- H1: 28px/300; body: 14px/400; meta: 11–12px

## Components
- Buttons: `border-radius: 0.25rem`; primary orange, secondary gray outline
- Cards: `border-radius: 0.25rem`, `box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)`
- Badges: pill (`border-radius: 100px`)
- Focus: `outline: 2px solid #D04A02; outline-offset: 2px` (WCAG AA)
